  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Enacts the \"smart meter transparency and consumer protection act\" in relation to requiring utilities to provide certain information about smart meters to customers; authorizes and directs the public service commission, in coordination with an independent third party, to conduct a study on smart meter implementation in New York state."
    }
